This project's agent documentation is the root `AGENTS.md` file. Read it before making any change. It is the single source of truth for:

- Project overview (Persian MoT encyclopedia, Nuxt 4 + Vite)
- GitHub Pages static deployment (`baseURL: /MoTDex/`)
- Directory layout (`app/`, `public/`, `nuxt.config.ts`)
- Dev server note (`TMPDIR=/tmp` on macOS)
- Agent meta-rules and skills index

Do not duplicate `AGENTS.md` content in Cursor rules. If a rule needs to change, change `AGENTS.md`.
